Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥君  就差最后一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做的事只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚  歌手绪方理奈小姐在工作地东央电视台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误饮有毒的茶后晕倒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被送往市内的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就检查结果来看似乎没有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方正在就人为和意外两种可能展开调查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…理奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要同情我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是别人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有时间考虑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式上场前一定会恢复的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听医生说  虽然是毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也就是洗涤剂或者漂白剂什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是少量的所以并不危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理也很及时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好路过的警卫员立刻叫了救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对喉咙有点影响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不会导致发不出声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因为精神上的惊吓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小英呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚就去了警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去自首…了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来嫌疑就能解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边就没什么麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和警方谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难看的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会影响接下来的节目录制的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了  今后就请您随意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那由绮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不需要担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任不管不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:06:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井先生  昨晚你让由绮小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤立无援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有给她帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为玛瑙小姐在？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是因为对方是绪方先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮小姐需要藤井先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不是障碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我的计划失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接近藤井先生你是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱我的人一定会因此而消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我还在由绮小姐的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样谁都不能接近…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有爱过你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有爱过任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不会爱一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:06:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为喜欢上我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  非常讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直  直到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有意义的  事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点晚了真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出犯人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是警察的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那推理研究会是干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴趣也好什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我想想看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道犯人是谁的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会有助于理奈的康复
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好像是医生的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是献给女神的最后一件礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底还是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么快就知道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是指这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是内部人员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方理奈什么时候会独处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会喝什么  都必须知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则连接近都不可能  更别说下毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我那时应该和她一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此  你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么体会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要摩卡来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那是吉力马札罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是蓝山？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡加上从由绮那里收到的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便我也尝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松山玛瑙认识由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出道之前  很早以前的由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见到松山玛瑙的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果由绮就在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和由绮是高中开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是学校的前辈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是的话  你也该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且玛瑙小姐要更年长一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们大四  五岁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是小时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说过吧  冬弥很小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了  那么小的时候我还没见过由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是见过  高中入学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥肯定会直截了当地说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“啊  由绮”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那可是遥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是遥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和玛瑙小姐在什么地方见过无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经知道了  我的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子走后门的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你教给我一个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小英去警察局了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须说个清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也讨厌一直含糊不清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然警方和媒体都说是三角告的密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的最后挣扎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么“拿着几幅画隐藏起行踪”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们早就被抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢  你才是受害者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连旗下歌手都保护不了  没用的经营者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用分手丈夫留下的画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要乘机霸占绪方事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就被那种哄小孩的玩意骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小英太单纯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果连妹妹的你都给卖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有这次的丑闻我这也已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想让玛瑙和你再加把油的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛瑙  女儿给了我最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗了你很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回公司去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛瑙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的关系对任何人都没有说过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重新来过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神崎社长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈小姐的病情如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和绪方社长是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于代唱事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛瑙小姐在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说几句
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丢掉的是金币还是银币？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉那个的话  就会全部忘掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不高兴的事情全部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后就由我来保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的身边不停改变样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论什么时候都是冬弥君的女神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后一直在看着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  完全从你的生活中消失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都看着你终究是也不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想先动些手脚  暂时也就不用看着了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果自己也忙了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里又一堆麻烦  也没办法去看你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  就是忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公会堂遇见你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一瞬间  就意识到“啊  是那孩子”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就唰唰唰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就叫做走马灯么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为要死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就大大地吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一句话竟然那么有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我是由女神组成的么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止在我面前出现的  女神们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全都是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全都是你的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想这样说  但是你也有你的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛没有被蒙蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然由绮是在计算之外的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么这么失望的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有很多美好的回忆了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那么小的小鬼的时候起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是为了冬弥君才做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭穿过去也是  曝光假唱的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是为了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到我来问了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥君  你那时候在找什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛瑙在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥生告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉住她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  快点放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这种便宜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本酒还是这种天天会喝的最好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶杯什么的都好  快点拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边喝酒边听你的忏悔很合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是现在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是至今为止的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天能帮我陪陪理奈么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像还没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:48.01,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}晚上就回来  玛瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对歌手绪方理奈小姐下毒一案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方于今天上午
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将就职于绪方小姐演艺事务所的经纪人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,28岁的犯罪嫌疑人仙道诚逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是对逮捕起到关键作用的举报人的证言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:25.25,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助逮捕嫌犯  举报有功者  平良木先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.28,0:21:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说他偶然在那个时间进了休息室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个歌迷  这种卑劣的犯罪是无法原谅的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经到这个时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.95,0:22:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈  我哪儿都不能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么有请森川由绮小姐演唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.85,0:22:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌曲是“恋色天空”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二十六页
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.87,0:24:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们坐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.22,0:24:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一动不动
